<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>API Documentation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .endpoint {
            margin-bottom: 2em;
        }
        .endpoint h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .endpoint p {
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>API Documentation</h1>

    <div class="endpoint">
        <h2>GET /job-description</h2>
        <p>Generates a job description for the given job title.</p>
        <p><strong>Parameters:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>jobTitle</strong> - The title of the job.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Example:</strong> /job-description?jobTitle=Software%20Engineer</p>
    </div>

    <div class="endpoint">
        <h2>GET /all-jobs</h2>
        <p>Returns all jobs as a JSON object. The job titles are used as keys and the job descriptions as values.</p>
        <p><strong>Example:</strong> /all-jobs</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>